720626f-a.title: Manhattan: Irving Place - 16th Street (East)
720626f-a.text:
33-25 Irving Place, and 116-14 East 16th Street, at and adjoining the
S.W. corner, builcings about to be demolished to make room for
two 12-story office buildings. The corner one will later be known
as the Nemo Building. 112-10-0B East 16th Street, also shown here,
will remain.
